webscript.description:
Creates a Stripe Session from a Cart to support a Stripe PaymentMethod lifecycle.  

    	Returns the sessionid for the stripe payment just created.

    	JSON Body sample:

    	{
		"cartItems": [{
			"id": "96a7d34f-7045-49f7-9e23-f6f1835cde94",
			"name": "Seed-Customer-SOW.pdf",
			"price": 1299,  //note price is in cents
			"image": "",
			"quantity": 1,
			"data": {}
			}, {
			"id": "8f04f8e6-6845-499b-85e6-d9d279bcc21f",
			"name": "LeftSide.docx",
			"price": 1299, // note price is in cents
			"image": "",
			"quantity": 1,
			"data": {}
		}]
		}
